\pard\f0\fs28 Shrubs or trees. Leaves simple, usually crenate or serrate, petiolate. Stipules free, narrow, more or less scarious, often deciduous. Flowers 5-merous, solitary or in clusters, umbels, corymbs or racemes. Petals pink or white.
